# ── Supabase / mini-BaaS connection ──────────────────────────────
# Kong gateway URL — leave empty to use the current origin.
# The frontend proxy (nginx in Docker, Vite dev-server locally)
# already forwards /rest/v1, /auth/v1, etc. to Kong.
# Using the same origin avoids all CORS issues.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY intentionally omitted — .env.local provides it
